{"tid":818692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2000萬買機掘未上市虛擬貨幣 投資者得米定得弊？","createTime":"2018-09-14T09:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T10:10:46.000Z","uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d306882fd694d77366b3fdf8424a9cd5fe05bd7","tid":818692,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"【蘋聞追click】2000萬買機掘未上市虛擬貨幣 投資者得米定得弊？<br />\n<br />\n虛擬貨幣高位回落，其中龍頭比特幣（bitcoin）由近2萬美元暴跌至現時約6,000美元，加上挖礦難度急升，成本上漲令不少「礦工」紛紛離場，神話看似迎來末日。一雞死一雞鳴，有人近大半年於社交平台高調宣傳變奏版礦機，以大硬碟容量碟取代高運算力顯示卡，力谷尚未上市的「filecoin」，聲稱兩年可賺八倍，集資最少2,000萬元。但新幣遲遲未上市，有投資者擔心發起人會「走佬」正要求退款；有專家則指新幣現時只屬炒作，籲投資者小心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-vzb3__2cG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-vzb3__2cG8&d=OnZiqc9BiKygMwPj5jzPgdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3d6c5833\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-vzb3__2cG8</a><br />\n<br />\n係youtube首頁見到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77651a7eaaaa8dcdde8aace3f7c3d3f0f45106a1","tid":818692,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5046cda5d63e607bc653f32bd6ece4f330c90469","tid":818692,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77651a7eaaaa8dcdde8aace3f7c3d3f0f45106a1","tid":818692,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:24:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講到尾就係要睇filecoin有無想像中咁多投資者入<br />\nd資金流哂係bitcoin到, 其他coin好難玩得起"},{"pid":"d5e2d840467e7c676cdd38a76109abc2f535b5fb","tid":818692,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"幣少爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1569a8a10d2d339c3b397a593865e4b9a5647b07","tid":818692,"uid